---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 首页
---
<section class="hero hero--garden"><img class="avatar" src="{{ '/images/avatar.jpg' | url }}" alt="晨汐的头像"><div class="hero__content"><p class="eyebrow">你好，我是</p><h1>晨汐</h1><p class="lede">{{ site.description }}</p></div></section>
<section class="garden-entries" aria-labelledby="garden-entries-title"><div class="section-heading"><p class="eyebrow">知识花园入口</p><h2 id="garden-entries-title">从一颗种子开始</h2></div><div class="garden-entries__grid"><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--individuals" href="{{ '/项目/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">🌿</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>项目</strong><span>完整项目，从零到一</span></span></a><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--reflections" href="{{ '/我的感悟/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">💭</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>我的感悟</strong><span>记录对 AI 的理解和看法</span></span></a></div></section>
<section class="recent-posts" aria-labelledby="recent-posts-title"><div class="section-heading"><p class="eyebrow">持续生长中</p><h2 id="recent-posts-title">最近更新</h2></div><div class="cards">{% for post in collections.recent %}<a class="card" href="{{ post.url | url }}"><p class="eyebrow">{{ post.date | displayDate }}</p><h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3><p>{{ post.data.description }}</p></a>{% endfor %}</div></section>
